Java Global Platform Shell (JGPShell)
=====================================

Installation :
==============

1) Make sure you have : 
 - java 1.4 (1.5 or higher to use th gui shell).
 - libpcslite 1.3.3 or later
 - libccid 1.2.1 or later
 - pcscd 1.3.3 or later


2) Unpack the files into a jgspshell folder

3) cd jgpshell
   ./compile.sh (or compile.bat for Windows users)
   ./run.sh (or compile.bat for Windows users)

More options :
==============

- To run the shell using the graphic mode :
./run.sh gui

- To generate javadoc :
./compile.sh doc

- to create a jar :
./compile.sh jar

- to clean the build foldr :
./compile.sh clean

- For more options :
./compile.sh ?
./run.sh ?

